🏥 Another Real Scenario: Hospital App
Situation:
A hospital uses a Patient Management System.
A new hospital branch opens → needs a new server.
Server must have: SQL Server + .NET App + Security Settings

Script to load what all the files and applications are required have to specify in the script

Now:
Launch EC2 #1  → Script runs automatically → Ready in 5 mins ✅
Launch EC2 #2  → Script runs automatically → Ready in 5 mins ✅
Launch EC2 #3  → Script runs automatically → Ready in 5 mins ✅
...
Launch EC2 #10 → Script runs automatically → Ready in 5 mins ✅

Total: 5 MINUTES for all 10 servers! 🚀


Example
#!/bin/bash
# Use this for your user data (script from top to bottom)
# install httpd (Linux 2 version)
yum update -y
yum install -y httpd
systemctl start httpd
systemctl enable httpd
echo "<h1>Hello World from $(hostname -f)</h1>" > /var/www/html/index.html
